Reiki II


Monday May 13th and 20th

 

7-9pm

 

Cost $200 for Level II, class meets twice ($50 for the Reiki Review)

 

Is it time to level up your Reiki? Going to Reiki Level II can change everything for you. Learn the Reiki symbols and how to do long distance healing. This level is a must for anyone already working “hands on” with people. Massage therapists, nurses, physical therapists, your clients will notice the difference! Level II is all about healing the emotional self and many people have breakthrough emotional healing experiences at Level II.

I will also be offering a Reiki review.

Can’t remember your Reiki?

Forgot your all your Reiki Symbols?

Or maybe you haven’t practiced all that much…

No worries! We got you covered. You can retake my Reiki class with me for just $50, wow! Brush the dust of your hot hands and lets bust out some Reiki moves so you can carry on healing the world with confidence.
